%% PROPOSED: Cross-Team ECO Handoff Sequence
sequenceDiagram
    participant HWE as HW Engineer
    participant PE as Project Engineer
    participant SW as SW Lead
    participant AUTO as Autonomy Lead
    participant AERO as Aero Lead
    participant QE as Quality Engineer

    HWE->>PE: Submit ECR for feature-driven change
    PE->>SW: Request software impact assessment
    PE->>AUTO: Request autonomy impact assessment
    PE->>AERO: Request aero impact assessment
    SW-->>PE: Return SW assessment
    AUTO-->>PE: Return autonomy assessment
    AERO-->>PE: Return aero assessment
    PE->>PE: Classify change and decide disposition
    PE-->>HWE: Approve, reject, or request rework
    HWE->>HWE: Implement approved hardware change
    HWE->>QE: Submit updated hardware for FAI
    QE-->>PE: Verification result and release recommendation
    PE-->>HWE: Release effectivity decision
